  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a wok or large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add ginger and garlic; sauté until fragrant, about 30 seconds.",
    "Pour in jam and stir-fry for an additional minute to release its flavors.",
    "Stir in bell peppers, carrots, celery, soy sauce, rice vinegar, and optional peanut butter. Cook for another 5 minutes.",
    "Add water; cover the pan and let simmer until most of the liquid is absorbed, about 10-12 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and serve hot."
